The old mine
According to tradition an orc becomes a warrior only when he receives an axe from the hands of a chief. The material for the axe the pretender should get in the mines of the Dead City...
#subobj 1
Find the entrance to the mine
The location of the mine is to the southeast of the orc fortress.
#subobj 2
Find the entrance to the old mine
The old mine is located just to the east of the mine. Don't forget that abandoned mines are home to undead.
#subobj 3
Get to the north tunnel
Only in the north tunnel can you get the right weapon material.
#subobj 4
Take the stone
The miners in the ore mine have done a good job at this location. The material is already mined, now you just need to pick it up.